FROM [Categories] AS [c]

    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]

) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]

    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]

) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]

) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]

) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0

FROM (

    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [Animals] AS [a0] ON [a].[Animal_Id] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Name], [a].[Id], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[Category_Id]
    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]

) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[Category_Id]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM (

    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]

    FROM [AnimalCategories] AS [a]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[Category_Id]
